                <seg xml:id="KR6d0001_T_003-0019a.11"><line>汝等若於無量億劫說不能盡。</line><tls:ann xmlns:tls="http://hxwd.org/ns/1.0" concept="YOU/PLUR" concept-id="uuid-b79e4679-292b-46e5-9458-f0cb20c8c894" xml:id="uuid-88dc99a3-82e3-4582-9c99-a382e33582d5"><link target="#KR6d0001_T_003-0019a.11 #uuid-2a3a6a0e-2a3d-490e-aa86-c532c59891b3"/><tls:text><tls:srcline title="妙法蓮華經" target="#KR6d0001_T_003-0019a.11" pos="1">汝等若於無量億劫說不能盡。</tls:srcline><tls:line title="Translation of 妙法蓮華經 into (en)" src="WATSON 1993 ">and though you and the others were to spend immeasurable millions of kalpas in the effort, you could never finish describing them.</tls:line></tls:text><form corresp="#uuid-10a28e3e-8167-434c-b264-dd96bbc7e215 #uuid-3c7c0022-58b5-4c2d-9c40-4f78d4da3bd6" orig=""><orth>汝等</orth><pron xml:lang="zh-Latn-x-pinyin">rǔ děng</pron></form><sense corresp="#uuid-2a3a6a0e-2a3d-490e-aa86-c532c59891b3"><gramGrp>
                    <pos>N</pos>
